skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: caffeine information
des:
Caffeine Information can tell you how many milligrams of caffeine are in some of your favorite products! 

When asking about products, use the brand name whenever possible for the most specific information. Caffeine amounts are based on standard beverage sizes and may not be accurate for large/small variations.

Try asking Alexa the following:

"Alexa, ask Caffeine Information for the amount of caffeine in a Red Bull?"

This tool does not provide medical advice, and is for informational and educational purposes only.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
